---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Privacy Policy — Velani"
  description="How Velani collects, uses, and protects your information."
  currentPath="/privacy"
>
  <a slot="nav-right" class="nav-back" href="/">
    <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
      <path d="M19 12H5M12 19l-7-7 7-7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
    </svg>
    Home
  </a>

<style>
.nav-back {
  font-size: .75rem; color: var(--ink3);
  text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: .03em;
  transition: color .2s;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .3rem;
}
.nav-back:hover { color: var(--sage); }

main {
  flex: 1; position: relative; z-index: 1;
  padding: 5rem 2rem 6rem;
}
.prose {
  max-width: 620px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.doc-eyebrow {
  font-size: .6rem; letter-spacing: .22em;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--terra);
  font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
}
.doc-title {
  font-family: var(--display);
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.6rem);
  font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.1;
  color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: .8rem;
  letter-spacing: -.02em;
}
.doc-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--sage); }
.doc-meta {
  font-size: .72rem; color: var(--ink3);
  margin-bottom: 3rem; letter-spacing: .02em;
}

.short-version {
  background: var(--surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--border2);
  border-left: 3px solid var(--sage);
  border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
  padding: 1.4rem 1.6rem;
  margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
}
.short-version p {
  font-size: .88rem; color: var(--ink2);
  line-height: 1.75; margin: 0;
}

.doc-section {
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
  padding-bottom: 3rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.doc-section:last-child {
  border-bottom: none; margin-bottom: 0;
}
.section-title {
  font-family: var(--display);
  font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 1rem;
  letter-spacing: -.01em;
}
.section-sub {
  font-size: .82rem; font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: .08em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--terra); margin-bottom: .6rem;
  margin-top: 1.4rem;
}
p { font-size: .92rem; color: var(--ink2); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
ul {
  margin: .6rem 0 1rem 1.1rem;
  font-size: .92rem; color: var(--ink2);
}
ul li { margin-bottom: .3rem; line-height: 1.7; }
a { color: var(--sage); text-decoration: none; }
a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 500; }

.contact-block {
  background: var(--surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--border2);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem;
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: .6rem;
}
.contact-block a {
  font-size: .92rem; color: var(--sage); font-weight: 500;
}

@media (max-width: 640px) {
  main { padding: 3.5rem 1.4rem 5rem; }
}
</style>

<main>
  <div class="prose">

    <h1 class="doc-title">Privacy <em>Policy</em></h1>
    <p class="doc-meta">Last updated: June 2026 · Velani · Hamilton, Ontario, Canada</p>

    <div class="short-version">
      <p>We only collect information you choose to share with us. We never sell your information or share it for advertising. You can unsubscribe or request deletion at any time.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="doc-section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Who we are</h2>
      <p>Velani is an independent digital and consumer brand operated from Hamilton, Ontario, Canada.</p>
      <p>Velani creates digital tools, educational content, wellness experiences, and over time may offer physical products and related services.</p>
      <p>Questions about this Privacy Policy? Contact us at:</p>
      <div class="contact-block">
        <a href="mailto:hello@velani.app">hello@velani.app</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="doc-section">
      <h2 class="section-title">What we collect</h2>
      <p>We collect only the information needed to operate Velani and improve the experience. Depending on how you use Velani, this may include:</p>

      <p class="section-sub">1. Email address</p>
      <p>If you choose to subscribe to Velani letters, onboarding emails, product updates, or related communications. Providing your email is always optional. You can use parts of Velani without subscribing.</p>

      <p class="section-sub">2. Purchase and order information <em style="font-style:italic;color:var(--ink3);font-size:.85em;">(future products)</em></p>
      <p>If you purchase a digital or physical product in the future, we may collect information needed to process your order, such as name, email address, shipping address, billing details, and order history. Payment information is processed securely through third-party payment providers and is <strong>not stored directly by Velani</strong>.</p>

      <p class="section-sub">3. Anonymous website usage data</p>
      <p>We may collect anonymous, aggregated information such as page views, general site activity, button clicks, and traffic sources. This helps us understand what is useful and improve the experience. This information is <strong>not personally identifiable</strong> and is never tied to your identity.</p>

      <p class="section-sub">4. Messages you send us</p>
      <p>If you contact us by email or support form, we may keep that communication to respond and improve customer support.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="doc-section">
      <h2 class="section-title">How we use your information</h2>
      <p>We may use information you provide to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Send Velani letters, onboarding emails, and practical ideas for clearer days</li>
        <li>Deliver onboarding emails and product guidance</li>
        <li>Share product updates and early access</li>
        <li>Fulfill orders and customer support requests</li>
        <li>Improve the Velani experience</li>
        <li>Notify you of important service or policy updates</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We will <strong>never sell, rent, or share your personal information for advertising or marketing purposes</strong>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="doc-section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Consent and email communication</h2>
      <p>We comply with Canada's Anti-Spam Legislation (CASL), the US CAN-SPAM Act, and applicable European privacy laws (GDPR).</p>
      <p>We only send marketing or product emails to people who have provided consent through our forms or customer relationship where legally permitted. Every email includes a clear unsubscribe link. We honour unsubscribe requests promptly and within legally required timeframes.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="doc-section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Your privacy rights</h2>
      <p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access the personal information we hold about you</li>
        <li>Correct inaccurate information</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your information</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
        <li>Request a copy of your personal data</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To make a request, email <a href="mailto:hello@velani.app">hello@velani.app</a>. We aim to respond within 30 days.</p>
      <p>If you are located in the European Economic Area (EEA), United Kingdom, or similar jurisdictions, you may have additional rights under applicable privacy laws.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="doc-section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Third-party services</h2>
      <p>We may use trusted third-party providers to operate parts of Velani, including services for email communication, website hosting, payments, analytics, and product fulfillment for future physical products. These providers process information only as needed to provide their services.</p>

      <p class="section-sub">Email provider</p>
      <p>We currently use <strong>Kit</strong> (formerly ConvertKit) for email communication. If you subscribe, your email address may be securely stored on Kit's servers in the United States. You can review their privacy policy at <a href="https://kit.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">kit.com/privacy</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="doc-section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Analytics and tracking</h2>
      <p>We use privacy-conscious analytics to improve Velani. We do <strong>not</strong> sell advertising or use invasive cross-site tracking. We currently do not use Facebook Pixel or ad-targeting networks. Analytics tools may change over time as Velani evolves, but we aim to prioritize privacy-first approaches whenever possible.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="doc-section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Data storage and security</h2>
      <p>Velani uses reputable infrastructure and service providers to store and secure information. We take reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect personal information. We retain personal information only as long as reasonably necessary for the purposes described in this policy or as required by law. You may request deletion at any time.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="doc-section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Children's privacy</h2>
      <p>Some products in the Velani ecosystem, including youth-focused experiences such as <strong>Glow Up Club</strong>, may be designed for children, teens, or families. We do not knowingly collect personal information directly from children under 13 without parent or guardian involvement or consent where required by law, including under COPPA (US) and similar privacy protections.</p>
      <p>Where youth-focused products exist, subscriptions, purchases, and communications for children under 13 are intended to be managed by a parent or guardian. If you believe a child has provided personal information without appropriate consent, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@velani.app">hello@velani.app</a>. We will review and remove information where appropriate.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="doc-section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. If material changes are made, we will update the date at the top of this page and may notify subscribers when appropriate. By continuing to use Velani after updates are posted, you agree to the revised policy.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="doc-section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions, requests, or privacy concerns? We aim to respond within 5 business days.</p>
      <div class="contact-block">
        <a href="mailto:hello@velani.app">hello@velani.app</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</main>

</Base>
